Assam Corona Daily Report: 14 June (11:59 PM)

218 new positive cases of Covid-19 and 155 recoveries were reported today in #Assam today. Total cases in the State stands at 4118 including 1960 recoveries and 8 fatalities.

#COVID19India  #Covid_19 https://t.co/ReuemPxh7x
